summary: Dear @taylorswift , I have been listening to your music ever since your first album back in 2006 and now I can finally say that...
caption: Dear @taylorswift , I have been listening to your music ever since your first album back in 2006 and now I can finally say that I’ve seen you live! I’ll admit that one of the reasons why I wanted to learn to play the guitar was because you showed me how easy it was to take simple chords and make something amazing. Thank you for writing songs that have been able to represent some of my feelings better than I could have ever done ❤ @taylornation

summary: One year after gorgeous came out is today. And I am able to post a selfie now and say I truly feel gorgeous in this photo. When...
body: One year after gorgeous came out is today. And I am able to post a selfie now and say I truly feel gorgeous in this photo. When gorgeous originally came out I did not post a picture because all of my selfies I did not feel pretty in. I believe that was because I was faking my happiness for a picture to go on the Internet. I now know I can never do that. This is from reptour Gillette night three before Charli XCX came on. I had just arrived to the stadium with my mom and I could not have been happier. I am happy to say gorgeous has been out for a year, I am more confident now. And also y’all are so so so gorgeous! @taylorswift @taylornation
